title: Music review: Powerful, showy performance in reunion of Mischa Maisky and Han-Na Chang
title_page: Music review: Powerful, showy performance in reunion of Mischa Maisky and Han-Na Chang | The Straits Times
maintext:
Victoria Concert Hall
Friday, 7.30pm
In one of the most anticipated programmes of the 2023/24 Season, South Korean conductor Han-Na Chang returned to conduct the Singapore Symphony Orchestra, with Israeli cellist Mischa Maisky as soloist.
